---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Cooking Spot"
  description="Cooking Spot - An open platform for discovering, sharing, and creating personalized cooking recipes. Join us and explore the future of cooking!"
  image="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
  <div class="content">
    <section class="py-6">
      <h1>Welcome to Cooking Spot</h1>
      <p class="text-responsive">
        Cooking Spot is an <strong>open platform</strong> designed for food enthusiasts,
        home cooks, and professional chefs alike. Whether you're looking for inspiration,
        sharing your own recipes, or planning your meals, Cooking Spot is here to
        make cooking easier, more fun, and tailored to your needs.
      </p>

      <!-- Hero Image: A vibrant cooking scene -->
      <img
        src="/assets/images/cooking-hero.jpg"
        alt="A vibrant kitchen scene with fresh ingredients, a chef preparing a meal, and a variety of colorful dishes on the table."
        class="rounded-lg shadow-md my-6 mx-auto w-[80%]"
      />
    </section>

    <section class="py-6">
      <h2>Why Choose Cooking Spot?</h2>
      <p class="text-responsive">
        Cooking Spot is more than just a recipe website. It's a community-driven
        platform that empowers you to explore, create, and share culinary
        experiences. Here's what makes us unique:
      </p>

      <div class="grid-3-col">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Discover Recipes</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Explore a vast collection of recipes from around the world. Filter
            by cuisine, dietary preferences, or ingredients to find exactly what
            you're craving.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Share Your Creations</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Have a favorite recipe? Share it with the community! Cooking Spot is
            an open platform where everyone can contribute and inspire others.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Personalized Meal Plans</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Coming soon! Create custom meal plans tailored to your dietary
            needs, whether you're focusing on protein intake, weight loss, or
            general wellness.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image: A diverse collection of recipes -->
      <img
        src="/assets/images/recipe-collection.jpg"
        alt="A diverse collection of recipes displayed on a table, including salads, soups, and main dishes."
        class="rounded-lg shadow-md my-6 mx-auto w-[80%]"
      />
    </section>

    <section class="py-6">
      <h2>Features That Make Cooking Spot Stand Out</h2>
      <ul class="text-responsive">
        <li>
          <strong>Open Platform:</strong> Anyone can contribute recipes, making it
          a rich and diverse resource for all food lovers.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Advanced Search:</strong> Find recipes by ingredients, dietary
          restrictions, or cooking time.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Community Interaction:</strong> Rate, comment, and share recipes
          with others in the Cooking Spot community.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Future Plans:</strong> We're working on features like personalized
          diet plans, daily nutrition recommendations, and more!
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Image: A chef preparing a meal -->
      <img
        src="/assets/images/chef-preparing-meal.jpg"
        alt="A professional chef preparing a meal in a modern kitchen, showcasing the art of cooking."
        class="rounded-lg shadow-md my-6 mx-auto w-[80%]"
      />
    </section>

    <section class="py-6">
      <h2>Our Vision for the Future</h2>
      <p class="text-responsive">
        At Cooking Spot, we're constantly evolving to meet the needs of our
        users. Here's what we're working on:
      </p>
      <div class="grid-3-col">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Personalized Diet Plans</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Create custom meal plans based on your goals, whether it's weight
            loss, muscle gain, or maintaining a balanced diet.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Daily Nutrition Recommendations</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Get tailored daily nutrition advice to help you meet your health and
            wellness goals.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Interactive Cooking Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Coming soon! Step-by-step cooking guides, timers, and ingredient
            substitutions to make cooking even easier.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-6">
      <h2>Join the Cooking Spot Community</h2>
      <p class="text-responsive">
        Whether you're here to find inspiration, share your recipes, or plan
        your meals, Cooking Spot is the place for you. <a
          href="#"
          class="text-primary hover:text-secondary transition-all"
          >Sign up today</a
        > and start your culinary journey with us!
      </p>

      <!-- Image: A happy family cooking together -->
      <img
        src="/assets/images/family-cooking.jpg"
        alt="A happy family cooking together in a cozy kitchen, showcasing the joy of shared cooking experiences."
        class="rounded-lg shadow-md my-6 mx-auto w-[80%]"
      />
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
